Body:
Description: Hello

Can you provide me with a link to download the Power BI Report Pack for Active Directory and Filesystem.

I have looked on the website and product pages but couldnt find it.

Thanks
Warren

@Saqib Sharif​ This ticket had originally gone to the Netwrix Auditor queue. I believe the customer is wanting to know about Power BI reporting module for Active Directory but I wasn't positive so I didn't want to send it to the customer. I decided to let the experts handle it.

What We've Learned Updated: The customer wants to know, from where they can download Power BI packs:

To download the Power BI Report Pack for FileSystem and Active Directory:
Login to Netwrix Customer Portal (Sign In)
Navigate to Netwrix Access Analyzer and expand it by clicking on "Download" button.
Afterwards, click on "Version Netwrix Enterprise Auditor Add-ons".
In there, you will see the Power BI packs for download.
Next Steps Updated: Awaiting customer's response if they require help with anything else.
